OL,3,CDVD and Blu-Ray sales up despite
OL,4,Cstreaming boom, says HMV boss
OL,6,FThe boss of HMV has said more shoppers
OL,7,Fare buying physical movies and TV
OL,8,Fshows again despite the recent
OL,9,Fstreaming boom.
OL,11,FBlu-ray and DVD sales are back in
OL,12,Fgrowth after significant decline in
OL,13,Frecent years, sparked by the rise of
OL,14,Fstreaming platforms such as Netflix
OL,15,Fand Disney+.
OL,17,FPhil Halliday, managing director of
OL,18,FHMV, said the retailer is "good
OL,19,Fhealth", with all its core product
OL,20,Fareas back in growth despite a
OL,21,Fchallenging consumer backdrop.
