OL,3,CDVD and Blu-Ray sales up despite
OL,4,Cstreaming boom, says HMV boss
OL,6,FHe said the recovery of its "physical
OL,7,Fvisual" business has been a particular
OL,8,Fhighlight, with collectors helping to
OL,9,Fsupport increased sales.
OL,11,FMr Halliday added that the category
OL,12,Fhas grown as households have witnessed
OL,13,Fan increase in the number of streaming
OL,14,Fservices, uncertainty over which shows
OL,15,For films are on certain platforms, and
OL,16,Frises in the price of many
OL,17,Fsubscriptions.
