OL,3,CDVD and Blu-Ray sales up despite
OL,4,Cstreaming boom, says HMV boss
OL,6,FThe managing director said: "It's been
OL,7,Freally positive to see the physical
OL,8,Fproducts in visual back in growth ` 4K
OL,9,Fand Blu-Ray have been doing
OL,10,Fparticularly well.
OL,12,F"It's a bit like people buying music
OL,13,Fphysically, in that we are getting a
OL,14,Flot of people wanting to collect
OL,15,Fcertain titles. Releases have picked
OL,16,Fup as well, and we have some really
OL,17,Fgood titles like Challengers coming
OL,18,Fout at the moment.
