OL,3,CDVD and Blu-Ray sales up despite
OL,4,Cstreaming boom, says HMV boss
OL,6,F"When streaming first came out I think
OL,7,Fa lot of people saw it as cheap and
OL,8,Fwith huge breadth of choice, but I'm
OL,9,Fnot sure people see it like that now.
OL,11,F"People are willing to pay for a
OL,12,Fphysical copy of shows or films they
OL,13,Fknow they will rewatch."
OL,15,FHe said this adds to strong recent
OL,16,Ftrading for music, technology and
OL,17,Fmerchandise across its 120 stores
OL,18,Facross the UK and Europe.
